---
// Sección de Servicios Inmobiliarios + Magna Servicios Integrales
---

<!-- ============================
     SERVICIOS INMOBILIARIOS
     ============================ -->
<section id="servicios" class="section-services">
  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="section-header animate-fadeInUp">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Lo que hacemos</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Servicios Inmobiliarios</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Acompañamos cada etapa de tu proceso inmobiliario con profesionalismo y transparencia.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <!-- Alquiler -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fadeInUp delay-100">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
            <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">Alquiler</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">Encontramos el inquilino ideal para tu propiedad o el hogar que buscás, con gestión integral del proceso.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Venta -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fadeInUp delay-200">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6"/>
            <path d="M18.09 10.37A6 6 0 1 1 10.34 18"/>
            <path d="M7 6h1v4"/>
            <path d="m16.71 13.88.7.71-2.82 2.82"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">Compra y Venta</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">Tasamos tu propiedad al valor real del mercado y gestionamos la operación de inicio a fin.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tasación -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fadeInUp delay-300">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/>
            <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">Tasación</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">Evaluación profesional del valor de tu inmueble basada en el mercado actual de la región.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Administración -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fadeInUp delay-400">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">Administración</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">Nos hacemos cargo de la gestión mensual de tus alquileres: cobros, rendiciones y seguimiento de contratos.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Contratos -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fadeInUp delay-100">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/>
            <polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">Contratos</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">Redacción y asesoramiento en contratos de locación y boletos de compra-venta con respaldo legal.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Boletos -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fadeInUp delay-200">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">Boletos de Compra-Venta</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">Gestión completa de boletos para asegurar y formalizar la transferencia de inmuebles.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================
     MAGNA SERVICIOS INTEGRALES
     ============================ -->
<section id="integrales" class="section-integrales">
  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="integrales-card animate-fadeInUp">
      <div class="integrales-content">
        <div class="integrales-badge">Unidad Complementaria</div>
        <h2 class="integrales-title">Magna Servicios Integrales</h2>
        <p class="integrales-desc">
          Mantenimiento, limpieza y reparaciones para hogares, oficinas y comercios. 
          Pedí tu presupuesto sin compromiso y recibí atención personalizada.
        </p>
        <div class="integrales-features">
          <div class="integrales-feature">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
            </svg>
            Reparaciones generales
          </div>
          <div class="integrales-feature">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3 2v7c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2"/>
              <path d="M7 2v20"/>
              <path d="M21 15V2v0a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v6c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h3Zm0 0v7"/>
            </svg>
            Limpieza profesional
          </div>
          <div class="integrales-feature">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="m3 9 9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
            </svg>
            Hogares, oficinas y comercios
          </div>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/0000000000?text=Hola%2C%20me%20contacto%20desde%20la%20web%20de%20Magna%20y%20quisiera%20solicitar%20un%20presupuesto%20para%20servicios%20de%20limpieza%2Freparaci%C3%B3n."
          class="btn btn-whatsapp integrales-cta"
          aria-label="Consultar presupuesto Magna Servicios Integrales por WhatsApp"
        >
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
          </svg>
          Solicitar presupuesto
        </a>
        <p class="integrales-insta">
          Seguinos:
          <a href="https://instagram.com/magna_servicios_integrales" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="integrales-insta-link">
            @magna_servicios_integrales
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="integrales-icons-deco" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="deco-icon deco-1">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3">
            <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="deco-icon deco-2">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3">
            <path d="M3 2v7c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2"/>
            <path d="M7 2v20"/>
            <path d="M21 15V2v0a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v6c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h3Zm0 0v7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="deco-icon deco-3">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3">
            <path d="m3 9 9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* =====================
     SERVICIOS SECTION
     ===================== */
  .section-services {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-brand-green);
    background: rgba(61, 83, 67, 0.1);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-brand-green-dark);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #666;
    max-width: 48ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 480px) {
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  .service-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 0.875rem;
    padding: 1.4rem;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-brand-beige-light);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-brand-beige);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .service-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(61, 83, 67, 0.1);
    border-radius: 0.625rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-brand-green);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-title {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-brand-green-dark);
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }

  .service-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* =====================
     INTEGRALES SECTION
     ===================== */
  .section-integrales {
    padding: 1.5rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .integrales-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-brand-green) 0%, var(--color-brand-green-dark) 100%);
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    padding: 2.25rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .integrales-card { padding: 2.5rem 3rem; }
  }

  .integrales-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .integrales-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .integrales-title {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 4vw, 1.8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .integrales-desc {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    max-width: 46ch;
  }

  .integrales-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .integrales-feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.87rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .integrales-feature svg {
    color: var(--color-brand-beige);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .integrales-cta {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-whatsapp);
  }

  .integrales-cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-whatsapp-dark);
  }

  .integrales-insta {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  }

  .integrales-insta-link {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .integrales-insta-link:hover { color: white; }

  /* Decoración con íconos */
  .integrales-icons-deco {
    display: none;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .integrales-icons-deco {
      display: block;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
  }

  .deco-icon {
    position: absolute;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }

  .deco-1 { top: -60px; right: 20px; }
  .deco-2 { top: 10px;  right: 70px; }
  .deco-3 { top: 50px;  right: 10px; }
</style>
